{"tid":2243202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【政情】「關愛隊」擬包括警察優先投票　政界憂令修例火上加油","createTime":"2020-10-14T14:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T09:47:03.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"2658b5b13f0581fa9deeab7b8bac438e974b12f6","tid":2243202,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T14:16:46.000Z","msg":"《政情》周二報道過，政府計劃修例推行境外投票。據了解，修例同時包括讓有需要人士優先投票的「關愛隊」安排。消息透露，對象除了老弱傷殘，政府同時考慮讓票站的工作人員，以至警察等紀律部隊，亦可優先投票，方便他們在投票日執勤。至於涵蓋的範圍有多闊，具體細節仍待落實。<br />\n<br />\n添馬艦消息透露，預料下月會將草案提交立法會。有政界中人指，優先投票選民包括警察，或令修例火上加油。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=409062\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D409062&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiQmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=b7ee423e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D409062&h=2f31437a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=409062</a>"},{"pid":"6e79bd78af2344e686165a1c785dfba30d3d0833","tid":2243202,"uid":137038,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T14:17:51.000Z","msg":"不如支持政府嘅可以優先投票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58ac021cd4b3827d5cc297f5cd35519e27ebf07","tid":2243202,"uid":152476,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T14:18:57.000Z","msg":"講到口臭<br />\n玩到咁肉酸不如直接委任啦"},{"pid":"5df2c93273b372f80296c41f28983d300eaf62bf","tid":2243202,"uid":53062,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6e79bd78af2344e686165a1c785dfba30d3d0833","tid":2243202,"uid":137038,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T14:17:51.000Z","msg":"不如支持政府嘅可以優先投票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T14:19:40.000Z","msg":"唔支持政府要等夜晚9點先入得，投唔切你的事"},{"pid":"22e8f3a0640bdd453e79989813a70ab6fe6d84ed","tid":22432